#: inc/customizer.php:121
msgid "An engraved ornament printed faintly behind the nameplate — a furled flag, a botanical plate, a coat of arms. Use a PNG with a transparent background and dark line-work: the theme tints it with the ink colour and fades it into the paper. Leave empty for no device."
